'''The Topps Company''', also known as '''Topps Collectibles''', or simply '''Topps''', is a collectibles company based in [[Wikipedia:New York City|New York City]]. It is best known as a leading producer of baseball cards and other sports-related trading cards, but it has also maintained a partnership with [[Lucasfilm]] since 1977, regularly releasing numerous series of ''[[Star Wars]]'' trading cards.

Topps also published ''[[Star Wars Galaxy Magazine]]'', its successor ''[[Star Wars Galaxy Collector]]'', a trading card game titled ''[[Star Wars PocketModel TCG]]'' (through its subsidiary [[WizKids Games]]), and several [[Star Wars comic books|''Star Wars'' comic books]].

Starting in [[2015]], the original trading-card series were reprinted in several hardcover volumes by [[Abrams Books]]. The first in the series was ''[[Star Wars: The Original Topps Trading Card Series, Volume One]]''.

